<div  class="layer-boiler">
      
<div  class="container">
      
<div  class="layer-boiler--container">
                      <h2 class="layer-boiler--title field__item">
        FROM FEBRUARY 2020 ONWARDS, BUREAU VERITAS PRESS RELEASES, FINANCIAL PRESENTATIONS AND REPORTS ARE CERTIFIED VIA WIZTRUST.
            </h2>
      
<div  class="layer-boiler--content">
                      <div class="layer-boiler--desc field__item">
        <p>TO CHECK THE AUTHENTICITY OF A DOCUMENT, GO TO <a href="https://www.wiztrust.com"><img alt="wiztrust logo" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="68af3a5e-1536-49e9-85a5-71b965219be3" height="26" src="/sites/g/files/zypfnx196/files/inline-images/logo-wiztrust-noir.png" width="113" /></a></p>
            </div>
      
